  "instructions": [
    "Heat 10g of coconut oil in a small pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and mustard seeds and let them sizzle for 10 seconds.",
    "Add 2-3 whole red chili peppers and let them sizzle for 10 seconds.",
    "Add 10-12 curry leaves and let them wilt for 10 seconds.",
    "Add 2-inch piece of ginger and let it cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 2-3 minced garlic cloves and let it cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 1 tsp of dashi powder and mix well.",
    "Add 250g of freshly ground pistachios and mix well.",
    "Cook for 3-4 minutes or until the pistachios are toasted and fragrant.",
    "Season with salt to taste."
